### 2. **No Data Validation or Sanitization**
**In Task Model (<mcfile name="task_model.dart" path="lib\\models\\task_model.dart"></mcfile>):**
```dart
factory Task.fromJson(Map<String, dynamic> json) {
  return Task(
    id: json['id'],
    title: json['title'], // No validation - could be null, empty, or malicious
    isCompleted: json['isCompleted'] ?? false,
    isHighPriority: json['isHighPriority'] ?? false,
    column: json['column'] ?? 'To Do',
  );
}
```

